OL,3,CHarry and Meghan to bring children
OL,4,CArchie and Lilibet to UK in July
OL,6,FHarry and Meghan to bring their
OL,7,Fchildren Archie and Lilibet to the UK
OL,8,Fin July, ITV News understands.
OL,10,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex will be
OL,11,Fvisiting the UK for the one-year
OL,12,Fcountdown to the Invictus Games which
OL,13,Fare being held in Birmingham. They are
OL,14,Fbelieved to be bringing their son,
OL,15,Fseven, and daughter, five, for the
OL,16,Ffirst time in four years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
