OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781707674
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan to bring children
OL,4,CArchie and Lilibet to UK in July
OL,6,FAfter losing his legal battle with the
OL,7,FHome Office over his security
OL,8,Farrangements when in the country last
OL,9,Fyear, the duke said he "can't see a
OL,10,Fworld in which I would be bringing my
OL,11,Fwife and children back to the UK".
OL,13,FHe has reportedly been assured that
OL,14,Fadequate security will be provided for
OL,15,Fthe upcoming trip.
