OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781707674
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan to bring children
OL,4,CArchie and Lilibet to UK in July
OL,6,FKing Charles has not seen his
OL,7,Fgrandchildren in person since they
OL,8,Fwere last in the UK in 2022 for Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth II's Platinum Jubilee
OL,10,Fcelebrations. It is not known whether
OL,11,Fhis father, the King, will have time
OL,12,Fto meet the children.
OL,14,FThe visit, as first reported by The
OL,15,FTelegraph, follows several accusations
OL,16,Ffrom Harry about his family in his
OL,17,Fmemoir Spare and television interviews.
OL,19,FA source told The Telegraph that there
OL,20,Fhad been a "warming of the frost"
OL,21,Fbetween the duke and his father.
OL,26,@|D@LOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
