OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781707674
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan to bring children
OL,4,CArchie and Lilibet to UK in July
OL,6,FThe duke lost an appeal last year
OL,7,Fchallenging the dismissal of his High
OL,8,FCourt claim against the Home Office
OL,9,Fover the decision of Ravec that he
OL,10,Fshould receive a different degree of
OL,11,Ftaxpayer-funded protection when in the
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex left
OL,15,Fthe UK and first moved to Canada, and
OL,16,Fthen California, after announcing they
OL,17,Fwanted to step back as senior royals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
